Detailed Description

This module contains routines and classes for the processing of command line arguments.

Enumeration Type Documentation

enum LEVEL_BASE::STAT_TYPE

Types of STAT's

Functions that need to iterate over all stats can use this to determine the type

Enumerator
STAT_TYPE_INVALID 

Invalid.

STAT_TYPE_SINGLE 

Simple stat with a single value.

STAT_TYPE_SD 

Holds static and dynamic count.

STAT_TYPE_BA 

Holds a before and after count.

STAT_TYPE_NORM 

Holds a count normalized to another stat, displayed as a ratio.

STAT_TYPE_DIST 

Holds a distribution.
